BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 179.28 740 Td (Chapter 1: What You Need to Start) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 70 725 m 542 725 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 700 Td (Crochet requires only two things: a hook and some yarn. That is truly all.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 676 Td (Start with a medium weight yarn, also called worsted weight or category 4.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 652 Td (Acrylic yarn is the best choice for beginners: affordable, easy to work with, and washable.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 628 Td (Choose a light-colored yarn so you can see your stitches clearly as you learn.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 604 Td (A 5mm or size H/8 crochet hook pairs perfectly with medium weight yarn.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 580 Td (Aluminum hooks are smooth and affordable. They are ideal for your first projects.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 556 Td (You will also want a pair of scissors and a yarn needle for finishing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 532 Td (A stitch marker \(or a safety pin\) helps you track where rows begin.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 508 Td (You can find all beginner supplies at craft stores or online for under 15 dollars.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 484 Td (Avoid dark colored yarn, fluffy yarn, or very thin yarn when starting out.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 460 Td (Your total investment to start crocheting is less than a single dinner out.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 436 Td (Once you learn the basics, you will have a relaxing hobby that produces beautiful gifts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 303.6 40 Td (1) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
