BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 676 Td (Next stitches to learn: treble crochet, shell stitch, and bobble stitch.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 652 Td (YouTube has thousands of free crochet tutorials showing stitches in real time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 628 Td (Ravelry.com is a free community with hundreds of thousands of free patterns.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 604 Td (Start with amigurumi \(stuffed animals\) if you enjoy small, quick projects.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 580 Td (Try blankets if you want a relaxing, repetitive project for watching television.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 556 Td (Join a local crochet group or online community for support and inspiration.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 532 Td (Challenge yourself to learn one new stitch or technique each month.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 508 Td (Keep a project journal noting what you made, yarn used, and lessons learned.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 484 Td (Gift your practice pieces. Handmade items are treasured by people who love you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 460 Td (Crochet is a lifelong skill that reduces stress and creates beautiful items.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 60 436 Td (You have everything you need to begin. Pick up your hook and start creating!) Tj ET
